distr<-"dexp"
proc<-"sign"
es<-0.05
parm_two<-1
  find.n<-function(x)abs(onesam.power(dist=distr, test=proc, n=x, parm1=es, parm2=parm_two, draws=10000)-.8)
result<-optimize(find.n, c(1450,1900), tol = 0.001)
dat<-as.data.frame(t(as.matrix(unlist(result))))
dat$dist<-distr
dat$test<-proc
dat$es<-es
write.table(dat, paste(c("C:\\Users\\grant_morgan\\Box Sync\\Research\\Mike Seaman\\minimum.csv")), append=TRUE, sep=",")
